\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underline{x}_{k+1}=\underline{x}_{k}+\alpha\underline{d}_{k},\quad\underline{d}_{k}\coloneqq\underline{r}_{k}-\beta\underline{d}_{k-1}
\]

\end_inset

其中系数 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset

